🎯 Revision Hook
When revising:

“Minimum coins to target” → DP with unbounded knapsack.

Formula: dp[i] = min(dp[i], dp[i-c] + 1)

If unreachable → -1.

👉 Memory trick:
“Build dp from 0 to X, each coin extends reachable sums.”
